description: See the difference between “ho hum” and WOW!  Much desired private patio, large enough for quiet dining or large party, sets #105 apart from all other Midtown condos.   This stunning home has all the updates a professional desires + the charm of being in an established building.  All new kitchen with quartz countertops, deluxe appliances, pantry, and breakfast bar leads to open living room with gas fireplace, hardwood floors and floor to ceiling windows. Roommate floor plan with an oversized bedroom with automatic shades and walk in closet.  Both bathrooms are updated. Tandem parking for 2 cars + extra storage cage in basement are included.  You can enjoy the pool, clubhouse and gym on a daily basis.  14th ST is an unbeatable location in the Heart of vibrant Midtown with the serenity of the Park on one side + the energy of the Arts District on the other.  Enjoy walking to an array of local restaurants, many events at Piedmont Park, the Beltline, the Arts Center, and Marta—offering direct access to the airport in just 24 minutes.  You’ll love calling #105 your home!
